# Carbon Pattern Library (before code)

**Playbook:** [`.carbon-kit/pattern-library/AGENT-RULES.md`](../../.carbon-kit/pattern-library/AGENT-RULES.md)

1. Identify screen type → `.carbon-kit/pattern-library/`
2. State pattern name + layout zones + actions
3. Map zones → `.carbon-kit/pattern-library/carbon-component-mapping.md`
4. Apply `.carbon-kit/knowledge/theme_implementation.md` rules 1–8
5. **Then** implement in `frontend/`

No matching pattern → add doc in pattern-library first. Never improvise layouts in code.
